main.java.embl.rieslab.emu.ui.uiproperties

Class TwoStateUIProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.embl.rieslab.emu.ui.uiproperties.UIProperty
      • main.java.embl.rieslab.emu.ui.uiproperties.TwoStateUIProperty

  • public class TwoStateUIProperty
extends UIProperty
    UIProperty that only accepts two states: ON or OFF. The value of these states are not known at compilation time and can be changed in the configuration wizard.
    Author:
    Joran Deschamps
